      "id": "PopularPost364258",
      "post_content": "This was the only card my uncle was missing from the Revised set, and he offered to trade a [Shivan Dragon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shivan Dragon) to me or my friends if we managed to \"pick the rose\" from one of our booster packs. My brother's friend Gregg drew the lucky straw the next week when we all took a trip down to the local Comic Book Store to get a few packs each, and so, because of Mana Short and a trade, he became the first of our little playgroup to own the mighty Shivan Dragon.  \n  \nNone of us at the time had any idea how good Mana Short itself actually was. Even without [Stasis](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stasis) or [Winter Orb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Winter Orb), this could cripple an opponent's tempo. Cast during your opponent's upkeep, and they probably wouldn't be able to play any spells until their next turn.",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost364258\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">This was the only card my uncle was missing from the Revised set, and he offered to trade a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Shivan Dragon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shivan Dragon\">Shivan Dragon</a> to me or my friends if we managed to \"pick the rose\" from one of our booster packs.  My brother's friend Gregg drew the lucky straw the next week when we all took a trip down to the local Comic Book Store to get a few packs each, and so, because of Mana Short and a trade, he became the first of our little playgroup to own the mighty Shivan Dragon.<br/><br/>None of us at the time had any idea how good Mana Short itself actually was.  Even without <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stasis\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stasis\">Stasis</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Winter Orb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Winter Orb\">Winter Orb</a>, this could cripple an opponent's tempo.  Cast during your opponent's upkeep, and they probably wouldn't be able to play any spells until their next turn.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '364258'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (2/18/2014 7:09:20 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
