    {
      "id": "PopularPost43205",
      "post_content": "This card is devastating. Combine with [Stasis](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stasis) or [Winter Orb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Winter Orb) and go bannanas. Hell, you can use it as a game winner in late game if someone is relying on a counter-spell to carry the day on their turn.\n  \n   \n5/5\n  ",
      "posted_by": "Gaussgoat",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost43205\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">This card is devastating.  Combine with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stasis\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stasis\">Stasis</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Winter Orb\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Winter Orb\">Winter Orb</a> and go bannanas.  Hell, you can use it as a game winner in late game if someone is relying on a counter-spell to carry the day on their turn.\r<br/> <br/>5/5\r<br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '43205'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy23116\">Gaussgoat</span>\r\n                                (1/19/2010 8:15:19 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt